{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Basically, there's a major demographic event going on."},{"time":4000,"text":"And it may be that passing the 50 percent urban point"},{"time":7000,"text":"is an economic tipping point. So the world now is a map of connectivity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15000,"text":"It used to be that Paris and London and New York were the largest cities."},{"time":20000,"text":"What we have now is the end of the rise of the West. That's over."},{"time":26000,"text":"The aggregate numbers are overwhelming."},{"time":28000,"text":"So what's really going on? Well, villages of the world are emptying out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40000,"text":"The question is, why?"},{"time":42000,"text":"And here's the unromantic truth -- and the city air makes you free,"},{"time":47000,"text":"they said in Renaissance Germany. So some people go to places"},{"time":50000,"text":"like Shanghai but most go to the squatter cities where aesthetics rule."},{"time":56000,"text":"And these are not really a people oppressed by poverty."},{"time":58000,"text":"They're people getting out of poverty as fast as they can."},{"time":61000,"text":"They're the dominant builders and to a large extent, the dominant designers."},{"time":65000,"text":"They have home-brewed infrastructure and vibrant urban life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67000,"text":"One-sixth of the GDP in India is coming out of Mumbai."},{"time":72000,"text":"They are constantly upgrading, and in a few cases, the government helps."},{"time":76000,"text":"Education is the main event that can happen in cities."},{"time":79000,"text":"What's going on in the street in Mumbai?"},{"time":81000,"text":"Al Gore knows. It's basically everything."},{"time":88000,"text":"There's no unemployment in squatter cities. Everyone works."},{"time":101000,"text":"One-sixth of humanity is there. It's soon going to be more than that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105000,"text":"So here's the first punch line:"},{"time":108000,"text":"cities have defused the population bomb."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114000,"text":"And here's the second punch line."},{"time":119000,"text":"That's the news from downtown. Here it is in perspective."},{"time":153000,"text":"Stars have shined down on earth's life for billions of years."},{"time":156000,"text":"Now we're shining right back up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}